description: I Gotta Q is New England's go to place for either a hearty breakfast or a plate of classic American bbq. They specialize in BBQ catering, fundraisers and  large events. Some of their featured items are pulled pork, tri-tip, brisket, baby back ribs and turkey and chicken legs. Everything is cooked in their on-board smoker and is sure to fall right off the bone!
name: GottaQ BBQ Food Truck & Catering
